    <div class="container">
        <!-- OVERVIEW SECTION -->
        <section id="overview" class="print-section">
            <h2>📋 Project Overview</h2>
            
            <p><strong>HealthCare Tracker</strong> is a production-grade patient management platform designed specifically for healthcare facilities in Africa (particularly Cameroon) to track HIV and TB patient appointments, medication pickups, and control visits.</p>

            <h3>🎯 Core Objectives</h3>
            <ul style="margin-left: 20px; line-height: 2;">
                <li>Track monthly drug pickup appointments for both HIV and TB patients</li>
                <li>Monitor quarterly viral load tests for HIV patients</li>
                <li>Monitor 6-month control checks for TB patients</li>
                <li>Send SMS reminders to patients for upcoming appointments</li>
                <li>Provide secure access for community and health workers only</li>
                <li>Maintain comprehensive audit logs for accountability</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>👥 Target Users</h3>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>👨‍⚕️ Community Health Workers</h4>
                    <p>Track local patients, manage appointments, send SMS reminders, record completed visits</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>🏥 Hospital Staff</h4>
                    <p>Oversee facility-wide patients, manage SMS campaigns, generate reports</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>📊 Supervisors</h4>
                    <p>Monitor adherence rates, analyze trends, plan interventions</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>🌍 Geographic Scope</h3>
            <p>Designed for deployment in Cameroon and other African countries. Supports multiple facilities, regions, and language options for SMS templates.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- FEATURES SECTION -->
        <section id="features" class="print-section">
            <h2>✨ Key Features</h2>

            <h3>Patient Management</h3>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Patient Registration</h4>
                    <p>Register HIV and TB patients with automatic patient code generation (HIV-001, TB-002, etc.)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Patient Information</h4>
                    <p>Store full contact details, demographics, emergency contacts, and health worker assignments</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Search & Filter</h4>
                    <p>Find patients by name, code, or phone number with advanced filtering options</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Patient History</h4>
                    <p>View complete appointment history and medical notes for each patient</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>Appointment Tracking</h3>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Automatic Scheduling</h4>
                    <p>System automatically calculates next appointments based on patient type</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Multiple Appointment Types</h4>
                    <p>Monthly drug pickups, quarterly viral load tests, 6-month controls</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Status Indicators</h4>
                    <p>Color-coded system: Red (eligible), Orange (upcoming), Green (on-track)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Appointment Records</h4>
                    <p>Document completed, missed, or late appointments with notes</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>SMS Notifications</h3>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Automated Reminders</h4>
                    <p>Send SMS 7 days before appointments with customizable templates</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Bulk Campaigns</h4>
                    <p>Send SMS to all eligible patients with one click</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Provider Integration</h4>
                    <p>Support for Africa's Talking and Twilio SMS services</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Delivery Tracking</h4>
                    <p>Monitor SMS delivery rates and failed messages</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>Security & Access Control</h3>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Worker Authentication</h4>
                    <p>Username/password login restricted to authorized health workers only</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Role-Based Access</h4>
                    <p>Different permissions for community workers, hospital staff, and administrators</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Data Encryption</h4>
                    <p>Patient data encrypted at rest and in transit with SSL/TLS</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h4>Audit Logging</h4>
                    <p>All actions logged with timestamp, user, and changes made</p>
